Kathleen A. O’Donovan OBITUARY

Kathleen A. O’Donovan Nov. 13, 1950 – Dec. 12, 2013 Resident of Concord Kathleen A. O’Donovan, 63 yrs. of Concord, passed away on Dec. 12, 2013. Born in Minneapolis, MN to Francis and Barbara (White) Corcoran, Kathleen lived in Concord for 35 yrs. She is survived by her husband of 39yrs. Edward O’Donovan, children Anne Marie O’Donovan and James Michael O’Donovan; brothers and sisters Maryjo Corcoran, Daniel Corcoran, Colleen Sullivan, Patty Estlander, Peggy Turk-Tilghman, Kevin Corcoran and John William Wiedner; grandson Dillon O’Donovan-Rojas. She was preceded in death by her son Edward James O’Donovan, Jr. Funeral Liturgy Sat. Dec. 21, 2013, 1:00PM at St. Dominic’s Church 475 East I Street, Benicia, CA. Burial will follow in St. Dominic’s Cemetery in Benicia.
